Kaneohe Bay Airshow

My exworker and I went to the Kaneohe Bay Airshow. We did get there a little late but were able to catch a glimpse of an F–22 Raptor which is capable of some pretty crazy maneuvers. This was followed by a Blue Angels demonstration who of course took off to the Top Gun Anthem.
